data.description: Spacious 3 Bedroom 2 Bath split floor plan stilt home built in 2004. 1,566 square feet of living space on a 5,000 square foot lot. Primary bathroom with shower and garden tub, covered parking with room to store your boat, new metal roof in 2020, tile flooring throughout. accordion shutters, downstairs enclosure with plenty of storage. Seller has an assumable mortgage aprox 270k at 3.5% (buyer has to qualify).
